long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Get ready to jump from wall to wall with a crazy cube on an endless platform. Make your highest score and show your skill. In the wall jumping game, you have to jump from wall to wall by passing through the rings. If you hit the ring, you will lose the game. 

That's why you should give full attention to the wall jumping game while controlling your character. In this game with an endless platform, if you collect the gold on the track with your character, you can get higher scores and prove all your skills in the wall jumping game.

How To Play
You have to use the mouse to move your character. You must pass through all the rings without crashing, without missing the rings.

Geo Dash Wall Jump Game Features
✓ Infinity level
✓ Easy control
✓ Little particle
✓ 2D Environment

Finally, you can enjoy these game for free (and more requests will be added)! Geo Dash Wall Jump Game extension does not contain any hidden ads.
